    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/bf3d356e2ab968c4718048e563319f8b.avif?t=1754411159\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br><br>作为岛上的新面孔，你此行的目的就是结识各路<strong>单身建筑</strong>，寻觅你的毕生挚爱！在这场匪夷所思的约会冒险中，你将与形形色色的建筑约会，享受一段独一无二的奇妙故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭晓隐藏秘密！</h2>岛上的生态丰富多样，处处藏着意外之喜！你可以探索幽邃的森林，也能征服白雪皑皑的山峰，或者干脆就静躺在鲜花盛开的田野中吧。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/95d108409ba2f5183c6e5a59ffbd5b11.poster.avif?t=1754411159\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/95d108409ba2f5183c6e5a59ffbd5b11.webm?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/95d108409ba2f5183c6e5a59ffbd5b11.mp4?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >写实的建筑移动！</h2>我们始终认为“约会模拟游戏<strong>唯一</strong>的缺憾就是没有<strong>波动冲刺</strong>”。于是我们果断将其添加到了游戏当中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/90d75a6869d219879631ecb3387431e3.poster.avif?t=1754411159\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/90d75a6869d219879631ecb3387431e3.webm?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/90d75a6869d219879631ecb3387431e3.mp4?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >去约会吧！</h2>想安定下来吗？来见见像米莉（一座风车，如果你态度好，也许会踩踩你哦）或者铁尼特（一顶四肢发达头脑简单的帐篷）这样的建筑吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/eef9887ef1724ffee174493a5fdd544a.poster.avif?t=1754411159\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/eef9887ef1724ffee174493a5fdd544a.webm?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/eef9887ef1724ffee174493a5fdd544a.mp4?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钓鱼也不错？</h2>俗话说得好，海阔凭鱼跃……只不过这款游戏里的海里头可见不着鱼。我们把鱼统统换成了车，这样才说得过去嘛。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/1c7f7d4ede14674c6b4939c070515286.poster.avif?t=1754411159\" width=590 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/1c7f7d4ede14674c6b4939c070515286.webm?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023890/extras/1c7f7d4ede14674c6b4939c070515286.mp4?t=1754411159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多精彩等你发现！</h2>将游戏添加到愿望单中，再加入我们的Discord社区，时刻了解最新动态吧！<br><br>",
